TitMainTitle: Four men, including one wearing light colored short sleeved shirt, belt, solid colored pants, ring, and watch, another man signing paper on desk, in interior with fan, opened door, desk organizer, typewriter, and calendar reading "Sunday Aug. 1, 1948" on desk, and sign reading "Daily Prayer O Lord help me to keep my big mouth shut, until I know what I'm talking about!  'Amen'"
